SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784031511
OL,3,CMasts of Second World War shipwreck to
OL,4,Cbe cut down in September
OL,6,FWork to dismantle the masts of a
OL,7,FSecond World War shipwreck packed with
OL,8,Fexplosives will begin in September,
OL,9,Faccording to the government.
OL,11,FThe three masts, in the Thames
OL,12,FEstuary, are part of the SS Richard
OL,13,FMontgomery, which sank in 1944.
OL,15,FAround 1,400 tonnes of wartime
OL,16,Fexplosives are on board the wreck,
OL,17,Fwhich is around 1.5 miles off the Kent
OL,18,Fcoast.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
